Title: .NET Switch Button Controls
Description: A simple .NET control that puts the Android, iOS and Windows 8 switch control. All made with vb.net in Visual Studio 2013.
HomeWiki:
New Door's .NET Switch Button is a simple VB.NET User Control that you can use to have Windows, Android and iOS-based Switch Buttons.

Version 1.0 has now been released. For help using this control, see our documentation.
